Code created for evaluation purposes.

Prerequisites :
C++ Complier (GCC recomended)
input file 'input.txt'

Compilation :
Go to the file you have saved the code.

and then use:
     g++ -o HwX.cpp -o HWX

afterwards use command:
    ./HWX

Everything should Run smoothly.

The program writes the analysis results to 'output.txt'.

Note programs assues that input file is well formed and contains less than 999 integers.

